Looking for a quiet, romantic and a fun getaway??? We got you covered !!!!

Only 4-5 hrs away from Delhi’s hustle bustle lies @ebcmussoorie at George Everest Mussorie. A beautiful glamping destination with all amenities,lip smacking food, a small trek and what not.

Whether it’s a romantic getaway or a small trip with your friends or family @ebcmussoorie has got everything for everybody. Whether it’s a cute picnic setup or a lavish barbecue dinner. The staff is so warm and hospitable, you would absolutely love your stay with them. 

So, 🔖 save this property and thank me later ❤️

#weekendgetaway #mussoriehills #romanticgetaway

latestPosts.caption:
Heart is full of gratitude because I am opening for @korolova.dj this Sunday @thanksandbeyonddelhi courtesy @nichoexperience @bhaskararora 🚀

She has inspired me to become a DJ, I have listened to her in sickness and in pink health, while working out in the gym to working late nights at the hospital. Music runs in my heart, ears, body, soul 🧿 and I am now opening for her. Could December get any better, this is the best birthday gift ever ✨Running high on emotions 🥹

Thanks to everyone who has supported me ❤️ imma make you all proud 💯 Seeyou all this Sunday, get your party shoes and groove on 🦩🕶️ let’s make it a night to remember 

@sahildeepbanga this set will be for you ✨

The ticket link is in my bio 🤝
